<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
   <style>

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .store-box {
            background-color: rgb(1, 1, 109);
            color: rgb(250, 94, 224);
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 16px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .store-box h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        .store-box p {
            margin: 6px 0 0;
            font-size: 13px;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }

        .steps {
            margin: 16px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }

        .steps li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

                body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: rgb(1, 1, 109);
            color: #dec1ff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
            /* background-color: #dec1ff !important; */
            color: #dec1ff;
            
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: rgb(1, 1, 109);
            color: #dec1ff;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
  
        .notice-box { background-color: rgb(1, 1, 109); color: #dec1ff; border-radius: 8px; margin: 16px 0; text-align: center; }
        .notice-box h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 18px; }
        .notice-box p { margin: 6px 0 0; font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.8; }
   
    </style>
</head>
<body>
        <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Account Deleted</h1>
            <p>Hello, <%= firstName %>!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>We are writing to inform you that your account on Nana's Pourfection Hub has been permanently <strong>deleted</strong> by an administrator.</p>

            <div class="notice-box">
                <h2><%= email %></h2>
                <p>✗ Account Permanently Deleted</p>
            </div>

            <p>Your profile, order history and all associated data have been removed from our platform. This action cannot be undone.</p>
            <p>If you believe this was done in error, please contact our support team as soon as possible.</p>
            <p>Thank you for being a part of our community.</p>
            <p>Best regards,<br>The Nana's Pourfection Hub Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Nana's Pourfection Hub. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>